properties.name: wg.interface.name
properties.description: Wireguard interface name (interface should be already created).

properties.name: wg.interface.default.mask
properties.description: Mask for peers created with default params.

properties.name: wg.inteface.default.persistent-keepalive
properties.description: Persistent keepalive for peers created with default params.

properties.name: wg.config.save.min-interval
properties.description: Maximum frequency to save wireguard configuration to file. 10000 means that saving will occur no more than once every 10 seconds.

properties.name: logging.api.max-elements
properties.description: The maximum number of logs that will be saved for access to them through the API.
